# UI TODO Plan (deep-dive, implementation-grade)

Base UI reference: https://github.com/oobabooga/textgen  
Comparable patterns to follow: Portainer (container operations), Grafana (metrics dashboards), Kubernetes Dashboard (multi-instance controls), Sentry (event streams), and GitHub Actions UI (job state transitions and action feedback).

## Product contract
- The UI manages multiple inference servers and one auto-launch daemon.
- The UI exposes operational controls, logs, metrics, and launch parameter management.
- The UI does not include chat interaction features.
- The UI supports desktop, tablet, and mobile layouts with complete keyboard support.
- The UI uses deterministic action feedback for every mutation (start, stop, restart, save).

## Chosen stack
- React 19 + TypeScript + Vite
- TanStack Query for data fetching/caching/invalidation
- TanStack Router or React Router v6.4+ data routes
- WebSocket primary realtime transport with SSE fallback
- Zod for runtime schema validation
- React Hook Form for dynamic launch parameter forms
- Recharts or ECharts for charts
- Component system: shadcn/ui (Radix primitives + Tailwind)
- Testing: Vitest + Testing Library + Playwright

