- [ ] B4. Implement optimistic updates for safe lifecycle actions with reconciliation.
  - Deliverables:
    - Pending state badges during start/stop/restart.
    - Rollback on mutation failure.
    - Post-mutation invalidation for authoritative backend state.
  - Pseudocode:
```ts
const startMutation = useMutation({
  mutationFn: startServer,
  onMutate: async ({ serverId }) => {
    const prev = queryClient.getQueryData(["server", serverId]);
    queryClient.setQueryData(["server", serverId], markStarting(prev));
    return { prev };
  },
  onError: (_err, vars, ctx) => queryClient.setQueryData(["server", vars.serverId], ctx?.prev),
  onSettled: (_d, _e, vars) => queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: ["server", vars.serverId] }),
});
```

